417
        unsigned int tov0 : 1;        /* Timer/Counter0 Overflow Flag */





418
        unsigned int ocf0a : 1;        /* Timer/Counter0 Output Compare A Match Flag */





419
        unsigned int ocf0b : 1;        /* Timer/Counter0 Output Compare B Match Flag */





420
        unsigned int : 5;





421
};
